    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless, displaying a deep, mirror-like shine with no scratches, dents, or imperfections of any kind. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery and trim showing virtually zero signs of wear. Mechanically, the car performs like new, with all systems functioning perfectly and a complete service history documenting its exceptional care. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and feels as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
