      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, offering a superior balance of proven performance and enduring value. This specimen has been curated to ensure mechanical integrity and features a well-preserved interior, reflecting a history of consistent maintenance. It represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a reliable, high-caliber driving experience. Available now for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 31500.0,
